---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-20 px-4 md:px-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-serif text-dark dark:text-cream opacity-0 animate-[fade-up_1s_ease-out_forwards]">
        Privacy <span class="italic text-coral">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl font-sans text-dark/60 dark:text-cream/60 mt-6 opacity-0 animate-[fade-up_1s_ease-out_0.3s_forwards]">
        Your personal data is safe with me. No weird stuff, I promise! ✨
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-12 font-sans text-lg text-dark/80 dark:text-cream/80 opacity-0 animate-[fade-up_1s_ease-out_0.6s_forwards]">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-dark dark:text-cream mb-4">1. Information I Collect</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          When you reach out via my contact form, I collect the basics: your name, email, and whatever lovely message you decide to drop my way. This is purely to get back to you and start our conversation!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-dark dark:text-cream mb-4">2. Cookies ✨🍪</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          I don't use aggressive tracking cookies. Any cookies used here are strictly necessary for keeping the site running smoothly and remembering your basic preferences (like whether you prefer the dark or light side of the web).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-dark dark:text-cream mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          I highly value your privacy. I will never sell, lease, or recklessly share your personal information with anyone. Our conversations stay between us!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-dark dark:text-cream mb-4">4. Reach Out</h2>
        <p class="leading-relaxed">
          If you have any questions about how your data is handled, feel free to drop me a line at <a href="mailto:hello@shree.com" class="text-coral hover:underline">hello@shree.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
